divs: Sighting Detailsstarted as one white object about twice size as star. height - unknown - appeared extreemly high in atmosphere. another white cicle appeared about miles south west of first white circle. second circle split up to aprox 5 smaller cicrles that went into formation and moved around - prinicipally staying in same location in sky...all diapeared within 5 minutes. visibility was excellent during event. there are 5 witnesses - we were on my sailboat at the time. the only reason i noticed the objects, was because i happened to look up the main sail, and the objects appeared directly overhead. i have excellent vision and extensive knowledge of aircraft - this was definately not anything i have ever seen
Summary: multiple circles - white - formations. very high altitude
